'''Tyrese Noslin''' (born 11 September 2002) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[right-back]] or [[right midfielder]] for {{Dutch football updater|Telstar}} club [[SC Telstar|Telstar]]. Born in the Netherlands, he plays for the [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao national team]].

==Club career==
===Early years===
Noslin was born in [[Amsterdam]] in 2002, but moved with his family to [[Almere]] at an early age. He grew up in [[Almere Haven]], living with his parents, younger brother, and two sisters. Noslin attended primary school at De Ark in Almere Haven. Reflecting on his childhood, he recalled: "I actually had quite a few hobbies besides football. I wanted to become a professional footballer early on, and when we played in the neighbourhood, I was always [[Ronaldinho]]. I'm still a real [[Lionel Messi|Messi]] fan." His early passion for football led him to join local club SV Almere, where he began his youth career.<ref name="ADW">{{cite news |last1=Mathlener |first1=Henk |title=Carrière Tyrese Noslin in stroomversnelling |url=https://www.almeredezeweek.nl/nieuws/sport/54654/carriere-tyrese-noslin-in-stroomversnelling |access-date=15 June 2025 |work=Almere Deze Week |date=29 November 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230205102846/https://www.almeredezeweek.nl/nieuws/sport/54654/carriere-tyrese-noslin-in-stroomversnelling |archive-date=5 February 2023 |language=nl |trans-title=Tyrese Noslin's career takes off}}</ref>

Noslin's potential was quickly recognised, and he joined the youth academies of [[Feyenoord Academy (Varkenoord)|Feyenoord]] and later [[AVV Zeeburgia|Zeeburgia]] before being scouted by [[Ajax Youth Academy|Ajax]].<ref name="ADW" /> He spent one year in the Ajax system before transferring to [[Almere City FC|Almere City]] in 2012.<ref name="ADW" /> There, he progressed through the academy ranks over the following decade. In the [[2023–24 Tweede Divisie|2023–24 season]], Noslin became a key player for Jong Almere, the club's reserve side in the [[Tweede Divisie]], scoring three goals in 22 matches that season.<ref name="WF">{{cite web |title=Tyrese Noslin &raquo; Club matches |url=https://www.worldfootball.net/person/pe643154/tyrese-noslin/club-matches/ |website=WorldFootball.net |publisher=HEIM:SPIEL |access-date=15 June 2025}}</ref><ref name="ADW" />

===Telstar===
On 8 August 2024, Noslin signed a one-year contract with an option for a second season at [[SC Telstar|Telstar]], competing in the [[Eerste Divisie]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Brood |first1=Thomas |title=Telstar presenteert drie nieuwe spelers |url=https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/339281/telstar-presenteert-drie-nieuwe-spelers |access-date=15 June 2025 |work=NH Nieuws |date=8 August 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240912151141/https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/339281/telstar-presenteert-drie-nieuwe-spelers |archive-date=12 September 2024 |language=nl |trans-title=Telstar present three new signings}}</ref> He made his professional debut on 26 August 2024 as a substitute in a 2–0 home win over [[Jong PSV]].<ref>{{cite web |title=PSV II vs Telstar 0–2: Summary |url=https://us.soccerway.com/matches/2024/08/26/netherlands/eerste-divisie/psv-ii/telstar/4367983/ |website=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |access-date=15 June 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250615090220/https://us.soccerway.com/matches/2024/08/26/netherlands/eerste-divisie/psv-ii/telstar/4367983/ |archive-date=15 June 2025}}</ref> Noslin scored his first professional goal on 27 October 2024, netting the winner in a 1–0 victory away to [[FC Emmen|Emmen]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Marck |first1=Christian |title=Tyrese Noslin blij met eerste doelpunt voor Telstar: "Vandaag is hij eindelijk gevallen" |url=https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/342084/tyrese-noslin-blij-met-eerste-doelpunt-voor-telstar-vandaag-is-hij-eindelijk-gevallen |access-date=15 June 2025 |work=NH Nieuws |date=27 October 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20241031192023/https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/342084/tyrese-noslin-blij-met-eerste-doelpunt-voor-telstar-vandaag-is-hij-eindelijk-gevallen |archive-date=31 October 2024 |language=nl |trans-title=Tyrese Noslin delighted with first goal for Telstar: "Today it finally happened"}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Dalsem |first1=Kees van |title=Tyrese Noslin (22) zeurde in begin nog wel eens op de training. Nu is hij fit en belangrijk voor Telstar |url=https://www.haarlemsdagblad.nl/sport/telstar/tyrese-noslin-22-zeurde-in-begin-nog-wel-eens-op-de-training.-nu-is-hij-fit-en-belangrijk-voor-telstar/23164088.html |url-access=subscription |access-date=15 June 2025 |work=Haarlems Dagblad |date=18 October 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20241226154107/https://www.haarlemsdagblad.nl/sport/telstar/tyrese-noslin-22-zeurde-in-begin-nog-wel-eens-op-de-training.-nu-is-hij-fit-en-belangrijk-voor-telstar/23164088.html |archive-date=26 December 2024 |language=nl-NL |trans-title=Tyrese Noslin (22) once complained in training, now a key and fit player for Telstar}}</ref> Operating primarily as a [[right wing-back]], Noslin became a regular starter during the [[2024–25 Eerste Divisie|2024–25 season]], making 32 league appearances and scoring three goals.<ref name="WF" /> On 27 March 2025, the club exercised the option in his deal, extending his contract to 2026.<ref>{{cite web |title=Telstar informeert spelers over contracten |url=https://sctelstar.nl/nieuws/telstar-informeert-spelers-over-contracten |website=SC Telstar |access-date=5 November 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250327093305/https://sctelstar.nl/nieuws/telstar-informeert-spelers-over-contracten |archive-date=27 March 2025 |language=nl |date=27 March 2025 |trans-title=Telstar inform players about contracts}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Brandhorst |first1=Stephan |title=Vlak voor de deadline bindt Telstar vier spelers een extra jaar |url=https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/347073/vlak-voor-de-deadline-bindt-telstar-vier-spelers-een-extra-jaar |access-date=5 November 2025 |work=NH Nieuws |date=27 March 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250330182426/https://www.nhnieuws.nl/nieuws/347073/vlak-voor-de-deadline-bindt-telstar-vier-spelers-een-extra-jaar |archive-date=30 March 2025 |language=nl |trans-title=Telstar extend contracts of four players just before the deadline}}</ref> Telstar achieved promotion to the [[Eredivisie]] via the play-offs, returning to the top flight for the first time in 47 years.<ref>{{cite news |title=Telstar-captain Mitch Apau viert geboorte zoon en promotie: 'Spakenburg of eredivisie, daar gaan we nog over nadenken' |trans-title=Telstar captain Mitch Apau celebrates birth of son and promotion: 'Spakenburg or Eredivisie, we'll have to think about it' |url=https://www.gelderlander.nl/eindhoven/telstar-captain-mitch-apau-viert-geboorte-zoon-en-promotie-spakenburg-of-eredivisie-daar-gaan-we-nog-over-nadenken~a23c28ae/ |access-date=2 June 2025 |work=De Gelderlander |date=1 June 2025 |language=nl}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=1 June 2025 |title=Telstar keert na 47 jaar terug in de Eredivisie, Willem II degradeert |trans-title=Telstar promoted to Eredivisie after 47 years, Willem II relegated |url=https://www.vi.nl/nieuws/telstar-keert-na-47-jaar-terug-in-de-eredivisie-willem-ii-degradeert |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250601180432/https://www.vi.nl/nieuws/telstar-keert-na-47-jaar-terug-in-de-eredivisie-willem-ii-degradeert |archive-date=1 June 2025 |access-date=2 June 2025 |work=Voetbal International |language=nl-NL}}</ref>

Noslin made his Eredivisie debut on 10 August 2025, starting in a 2–0 defeat away to [[AFC Ajax|Ajax]] at the [[Johan Cruyff Arena]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Ajax start eredivisie met moeizame thuisoverwinning op teruggekeerd Telstar |trans-title=Ajax open Eredivisie campaign with hard-fought home win over returning Telstar |url=https://nos.nl/artikel/2578198-ajax-start-eredivisie-met-moeizame-thuisoverwinning-op-teruggekeerd-telstar |work=NOS |language=nl |date=10 August 2025 |access-date=26 October 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250904085151/https://nos.nl/artikel/2578198-ajax-start-eredivisie-met-moeizame-thuisoverwinning-op-teruggekeerd-telstar |archive-date=4 September 2025}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Ajax 2–0 Telstar |url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/740983/telstar-ajax-amsterdam |website=ESPN |date=10 August 2025 |access-date=26 October 2025}}</ref> He scored his first goal in the competition on 5 October, netting in a 2–1 away defeat to [[AZ Alkmaar|AZ]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Moeizame zege AZ op Telstar, Oranjeklant Meerdink passeert keeper Koeman |url=https://nos.nl/artikel/2585347-moeizame-zege-az-op-telstar-oranjeklant-meerdink-passeert-keeper-koeman |access-date=16 October 2025 |work=NOS |date=5 October 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20251006101903/https://nos.nl/artikel/2585347-moeizame-zege-az-op-telstar-oranjeklant-meerdink-passeert-keeper-koeman |archive-date=6 October 2025 |language=nl |trans-title=Hard-fought AZ win over Telstar as Dutch international man Meerdink beats goalkeeper Koeman}}</ref>

==International career==
Noslin is eligible to represent [[Curaçao national football team|Curaçao]] through his heritage and played for the [[Curaçao national under-20 football team|Curaçao national under-20 team]] in 2020. He took part in the [[2020 CONCACAF U-20 Championship qualifying|2020 CONCACAF U-20 Championship qualifiers]], where he made an immediate impact by scoring in a 5–0 victory over [[Saint Martin national football team|Saint Martin]].<ref>{{cite news |title=Curaçao going for second win |url=https://www.sport.cw/curacao-going-for-second-win/ |access-date=15 June 2025 |work=Sport.cw |date=20 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250219122952/https://www.sport.cw/curacao-going-for-second-win/ |archive-date=19 February 2025 |language=nl-NL}}</ref>

